==English==
===Conjunction===
'''inclusive or'''

#(''logic, computing'') A [[connective]] joining two [[predicate]]s A and B that is true when at least one of A and B are true.

===Translations===
*French: [[ou inclusif]]
*Hungarian: [[megengedő vagy]]
*Swedish: [[inklusivt eller]] {{n}}

